6. Update decision log and iterations.json when complete

## Discoveries

- E2E tests failing due to error message format changes from error handling improvements
- The `cd_test.go` was fixed to expect the new error format `worktree not found for target 'nonexistent'`
- The `create_test.go` tests expect exit code 5 but get exit code 1
- Manually testing the binary returns exit code 5 correctly when run from the command line
- The test runs in a different context (project directory) and context detection may behave differently
- The single-branch fixture contains only a main branch - tests for "nonexistent" branches should work
- The context detector looks for `.git` file (not directory) for worktree validation
- Multiple wrapper blocks in shell config files don't get properly cleaned up (bug found during integration test)

